

* read pdb files

* add separate options for:
 - full surface grid

 ./sas_grid --file aaa.xyz (or pdb) --radius 1.3 --type surface --factor 3
 
 
 - box grid minus overlap surface
 
 ./sas_grid --file aaa.xyz (or pdb) --radius 1.3 --type box --centerx xx --centery yy --centerz zz --sizex 3.0 --sizey 3.0 --sizez 3.0 --dr 0.1
 
 or
 
 ./sas_grid --file aaa.xyz (or pdb) --radius 1.3 --type box --center xx yy zz --size 3.0 3.0 3.0 --dr 0.1
